<li style="text-align: left;">To add on ski/snowboard carriage and claim £100 discount, you must call our reservations team to book. This will not automatically apply on our website.</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">The offer can be added at any time during the offer period, as long as both items are added together. Offer is available from Thursday 13th June 2024, while stocks last.</li>
